      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Peradeniya ¶ Ceylon ¶ 4th March 1870 ¶ My dear Hooker ¶ [Discusses botanical matters]...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M70.03.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>George Thwaites to Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Directors' correspondence, vol. 162, ff 393-4</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Peradeniya</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Ceylon</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">4th March 1870</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Hooker</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">[Discusses botanical matters]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">…</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I heard from Moore of Sydney that, though v. Mueller continues the nominal Director of the Melbourne Garden, a Mr. Ferguson<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>William Ferguson.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is virtually the Director having charge of the work in it, and that von Mueller is now really only the Government Botanist, and that he is in low spirits about it. I wrote some time ago congratulating v. Mueller upon being relieved from the mere garden duties,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>thinking it would be a pleasant arrangement for him and not expecting it would have annoyed him. It makes one fear that his love of science does not sufficiently predominate over his appetite for κυδος<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>kudos.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">…</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">[Discusses botanical matters and field trips]</p>
         </div>
      </body>
